Welcome to The DL—an iconic three-level venue in the Lower East Side, making memories for 20 + years.​

Year-Round Retractable Rooftop

Let's be real—NYC has plenty of rooftops, but none hit quite like The DL. Our rooftop club brings together killer views, amazing music, and a crowd that comes to actually have fun. No pretentious vibes here—just the best rooftop club NYC has where you can dance under the stars with the Manhattan skyline as your backdrop.

Three Levels,
One Epic Night

Rain or shine, hot or cold, we're always open thanks to our retractable roof (yeah, we thought of everything). Bounce between our three unique levels depending on your mood—each floor has its own energy, but the good vibes stay consistent throughout

Sip, Socialize, Repeat

From creative cocktails that'll have your friends asking "what IS that?" to classic favorites done right, our drink menu has something for every vibe. And yes, our bottle service options are actually worth it—with packages designed for college budgets and special occasions alike.

IT'S MY BIRTHDAY!

The Lounge Energy You've Been Looking For

Our roster of resident DJs are masters of their craft, seamlessly blending genres from open format, infectious house grooves, and chart-topping hip-hop to keep the energy soaring all night long.


We are also a magnet for special guest appearances from internationally renowned DJs, making The DL a hotspot for discovering the freshest sounds and the ultimate DJ rooftop NYC destination. The music at our NYC rooftop nightclub is more than just background noise; it's an integral part of the unforgettable journey we offer every night.

VIP Birthday Packages & Private Events

Choose from our signature birthday packages including The Rivington, The Birthday Bash, The Ludlow, and The Delancey, each offering premium bottles, champagne, and VIP service. For larger celebrations, our private event options can accommodate groups of any size with customized food, beverage, and entertainment options.

The DL Rooftop Club: An Atmosphere Like No Other

The DL is more than just a club; it's a carefully crafted environment designed to stimulate the senses and create lasting memories. Our unique location in the Lower East Side club scene adds to our distinct appeal. 

Chic Decor and a Vibrant Crowd

Step into a space where chic, contemporary design meets sophisticated comfort. Our multi-level venue, including the stunning Third Floor Rooftop with its South Beach-esque decor and climate-controlled retractable roof, boasts stylish decor, creating an upscale yet inviting ambiance. The DL attracts a fashionable and energetic crowd, a diverse mix of New Yorkers and international visitors all seeking a premium nightlife experience.

Spectacular Night time Panoramas

Our rooftop offers truly spectacular, panoramic views of the Lower East Side and the broader Manhattan skyline. The glittering city lights provide a mesmerizing backdrop to your night, making every moment picture-perfect. Whether you're dancing under the stars or enjoying a quiet conversation, the views from The DL are an unforgettable part of the experience.

Ready for the Best Rooftop Club Experience in NYC?

Don't just dream about the ultimate New York City night out – live it at The DL. We're ready to show you why we're consistently named the best rooftop club NYC has to offer.

Frequently asked questions

The DL is a multi-level lounge, restaurant, and event space located in Manhattan's Lower East Side. Known for its luxurious ambiance and unique experiences across its three floors, it's a staple in New York's downtown cultural landscape.

The DL hosts a variety of events ranging from daytime events under the sun to nightlife scenes under the stars. We also feature themed events such as "Skip the Line" on Fridays and Saturdays and special holiday events.

To make a reservation or book an event, you can visit our 'Reservations' section on the website or contact us directly via email or phone.

We are 21+ venue with a strict "NO ID, NO ENTRY" policy.

-PROPER GOVERNMENT-ISSUED ID is required. -International and Domestic passports are accepted. -We do not accept foreign ID cards or drivers licenses.

*IDNYC cards are not accepted.
